2013年8月23日，作曲家丹·梅斯 (Dan Messe)，{{link-en|Hem樂隊|Hem (band)}}的創始人和成員之一，證實了他將與{{link-en|克雷格·盧卡斯|Craig Lucas}}和{{link-en|納森·泰森|Nathan Tysen}}合作，為《艾蜜莉的異想世界》的音樂改編作品創作配樂。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-23808207 |title=Amelie musical to be made for Broadway |publisher=BBC |date=23 August 2013 |access-date=25 January 2014 |archive-date=2022-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120135454/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-23808207 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Derschowitz |first=Jessica |url=https://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57599847/amelie-becoming-a-broadway-musical/ |title="Amelie" becoming a Broadway musical |work=CBS News |date=23 August 2013 |access-date=25 January 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130904045827/https://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57599847/amelie-becoming-a-broadway-musical/ |archive-date=4 September 2013}}</ref> 梅斯還確認他將為該節目創作所有原創音樂，而不是使用扬·提尔森樂譜。<ref name="broadway">{{cite news | url=http://broadwaytour.net/amelie-set-to-be-adapted-for-broadway | work=Broadway Tour | title='Amelie' Set to be Adapted for Broadway | date=26 August 2013 | accessdate=2022-01-20 | archive-date=2013-12-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207094504/http://broadwaytour.net/amelie-set-to-be-adapted-for-broadway }}</ref> {{link-en|艾蜜莉的異想世界 (音樂劇)|Amélie (musical)|音樂改編}}於2015年8月在伯克利話劇團（Berkeley Repertory Theater）首演。<ref>{{cite news|first=Robert|last=Hurwitt|date=14 September 2015|title=Fanciful Film Floats Dreamily Onto the Stage with "Amélie"|newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle|url=http://www.sfgate.com/performance/article/Am-lie-is-a-dream-of-a-musical-at-Berkeley-6500931.php|access-date=17 June 2016|archive-date=2022-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120135449/https://www.sfgate.com/performance/article/Am-lie-is-a-dream-of-a-musical-at-Berkeley-6500931.php}}</ref> 該音樂劇於2017年3月在[[百老匯|百老匯]]開演，並於2017年5月結束。<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.playbill.com/article/hamilton-39-s-phillipa-soo-will-star-in-amelie-musical-on-broadway |title=Hamilton's Phillipa Soo Will Star in Amélie Musical on Broadway |magazine=Playbill |date=17 June 2016 |first=Robert |last=Viagas |access-date=17 June 2016 |archive-date=2020-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914235114/https://www.playbill.com/article/hamilton-39-s-phillipa-soo-will-star-in-amelie-musical-on-broadway }}</ref> 這部作品於2016年12月在洛杉磯的阿曼森劇院（Ahmanson Theatre）開始了百老匯前的演出，由[[菲莉帕·蘇|菲莉帕·蘇]]擔任主角。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.centertheatregroup.org/tickets/ahmanson-theatre/2016-17/amelie-a-new-musical/|title=Amélie, A New Musical|website=Center Theatre Group|access-date=15 December 2016|archive-date=2022-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120174535/https://www.centertheatregroup.org/tickets/ahmanson-theatre/2016-17/amelie-a-new-musical/}}</ref> 

居內因厭惡音樂劇而與音樂劇保持距離，稱他只出售了為兒童慈善機構“{{link-fr|Mécénat Chirurgie cardiaque|Mécénat Chirurgie Cardiaque}}”籌集資金的權利。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/amelie-director-jean-pierre-jeunet-616611 |title='Amelie' Director Jean-Pierre Jeunet 'Disgusted' by Musical |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=28 August 2013 |access-date=25 January 2014 |first=Rhonda |last=Richford |archive-date=2021-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310184523/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/amelie-director-jean-pierre-jeunet-616611 }}</ref>

== 評價 ==
對於2007年的電視節目《[[生死一點靈|生死一點靈]]》，一個“古怪的童話故事”，[[美國廣播公司|美國廣播公司]]（ABC）尋求一種《艾蜜莉的異想世界》的感覺，與“奇思妙想、精神和魔法”相同的和弦。《生死一點靈》的創作者[[布萊恩·富勒|布萊恩·富勒]]說《艾蜜莉的異想世界》是他最喜歡的電影。“我喜歡的所有東西都在那部電影中得到體現”，他說。“這是一部讓我因善良而不是悲傷而哭泣的電影”。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》對《生死一點靈》的評論報導稱“《艾蜜莉的異想世界》對《生死一點靈》的影響無處不在”。<ref>{{cite news|first=Bill|last=Carter|title=A Touching Romance, if They Just Don't Touch|work=The New York Times|date=5 July 2007|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/05/arts/television/05dais.html|accessdate=2022-01-20|archive-date=2022-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220404204318/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/05/arts/television/05dais.html}}</ref>

